<h1>Edit Settings</h1>


<button><%= link_to "Close All Open Tabs", bar_path(@bar, bar: {close_all: true}, data: :success, :format => :js), id: "close-all", remote: true, :method => :put %></button>

<p>By hitting "close all open tabs", you'll be closing all the bar's active tabs for the night.</p>
<p>If you aren't tired, wasted, and closed for the night, and this isn't what you'd like to do, don't.</p>

<% if @bar.discoverable %>
  <button><%= link_to "Discoverable: OFF", bar_path(@bar, bar: {discoverable: false}), :method => :put %></button>
<% else  %>
    <button><%= link_to "Discoverable: ON", bar_path(@bar, bar: {discoverable: true}), :method => :put %></button>
<% end %>
